    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers reliable transportation for anyone seeking a functional car at a reasonable price. The engine and transmission are operational, though the car shows noticeable signs of wear both inside and out, including some minor cosmetic blemishes and interior aging. It has been used regularly and would benefit from a tune-up, but it remains a solid choice for a budget-conscious buyer looking for a dependable daily driver.",
