    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a collector-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a precision 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The chassis has been meticulously preserved, including a proactive rear subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings to ensure peak torsional rigidity. This vehicle retains its factory-spec limited-slip differential and double VANOS system, both functioning within tight tolerances. Every VIN tag is present, and the atmospheric induction note remains crisp, reflecting a lifetime of climate-controlled storage and rigorous preventative maintenance. A truly turn-key investment for the purist driver.",
